Class ModuleImpls

  • Object
    • AbstractCollection<E>
      • AbstractList<E>
        • ArrayList<Module>
          • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.ModuleImpls
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Module>, Collection<Module>, List<Module>, RandomAccess

    public class ModuleImpls
extends ArrayList<Module>
    A wrapper class for multiple implementations of a module. Since the device, name, and netlist should be all be the same, it offers convenience accessors to the first implementation if it exists. Created on: Jun 21, 2016
    See Also:
